      <title>哈格蒂表示，比特币必须在这里蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/bitcoin-has-to-thrive-here-hagerty-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[田纳西州共和党参议员比尔·哈格蒂表示，比特币和加密货币需要在美国蓬勃发展，在唐纳德·特朗普的领导下，这种繁荣将会实现。哈格蒂参加了“彭博监视”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/bitcoin-has-to-thrive-here-hagerty-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Viaro 同意从壳牌、埃克森美孚收购英国北海天然气资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/viaro-agrees-to-buy-uk-north-sea-gas-assets-from-shell-exxon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Viaro Energy Ltd. 同意从壳牌公司和埃克森美孚公司手中购买英国北海的多个天然气田，这使得这家私人控股公司首次成为该国的海上运营商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/viaro-agrees-to-buy-uk-north-sea-gas-assets-from-shell-exxon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼支持的科技创始人试图兑现他的“伯克希尔 2.0”承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-backed-tech-founder-tries-to-fulfill-his-berkshire-2-0-promise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大企业家安德鲁·威尔金森（Andrew Wilkinson）早年决定放弃记者职业，自学网页设计，这一决定带来了丰厚的回报，使他成为一家价值超过 3 亿美元的科技投资公司的大股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-backed-tech-founder-tries-to-fulfill-his-berkshire-2-0-promise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:15:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 的 Wilding 表示，美联储可能每季度降息一次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/fed-may-cut-at-once-a-quarter-pace-pimco-s-wilding-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pimco 经济学家 Tiffany Wilding 在彭博电视台表示，劳动力市场正在正常化，预计美国失业率最终将在 4.2% 左右。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/fed-may-cut-at-once-a-quarter-pace-pimco-s-wilding-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼在美国的 IPO 规模曾高达 250 亿美元，现定于 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-s-us-closed-end-fund-psus-eyes-2-billion-in-ipo-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 计划首次公开募股 (IPO) 美国封闭式基金，预计将募集 20 亿美元资金，这还不到这位亿万富翁对冲基金经理本月早些时候提出的募资目标的十分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-s-us-closed-end-fund-psus-eyes-2-billion-in-ipo-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于行业低迷，ADM 利润缩水幅度超过预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/adm-s-profit-shrinks-more-than-expected-on-crop-market-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于面临农作物市场的低迷，这家谷物贸易巨头阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司的季度利润缩水幅度超过预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/adm-s-profit-shrinks-more-than-expected-on-crop-market-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值致中国消费者赴日消费激增 普拉达销售额飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prada-sales-jump-as-chinese-shoppers-splash-out-in-japan-with-weak-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在奢侈品行业整体放缓的背景下，意大利时尚集团普拉达 (Prada SpA) 继续保持强劲增长，其销售额出现大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prada-sales-jump-as-chinese-shoppers-splash-out-in-japan-with-weak-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决定公布前，欧洲股市因稳健数据上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告显示欧元区上季度经济增长超过预期，投资者关注本周美国和英国央行的利率决定，欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储公布财报前股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员们仔细研究一系列企业业绩，并准备迎接对全球市场走势至关重要的央行决策，股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
